<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#fragment_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Fragment> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#glow_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Glow> ;
