        <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Eerie> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#moment_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#confront_1>,
