    ns4:Location <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#underwater_1> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#dwarf_1> a <https://w3id.org/framester/data/propbank-3.4.0/RoleSet/dwarf-01> ;
